'''布特萊薩特頓'''（Budleigh Salterton）是[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[德文郡|德文郡]]東部的一個濱海小鎮，位於埃克塞特東南15英里<ref name=AONB>{{cite web | url=http://www.eastdevonaonb.org.uk/ | title=East Devon Area of Outstanding Natural Beauty Website | accessdate=2012-08-27 | archive-date=2021-01-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127142511/https://www.eastdevonaonb.org.uk/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。據2011年人口普查，布特萊薩特頓有人口5,967人<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ukcensusdata.com/budleigh-e05003463#sthash.y9BeL5ay.dpbs|title=Budleigh ward 2011|accessdate=24 February 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303223141/http://www.ukcensusdata.com/budleigh-e05003463#sthash.y9BeL5ay.dpbs|archive-date=2016-03-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。
